ygData.msgSnippet: ... Br Z took me 3* 8 hour session and 3* 2 hours session to find. Br Qwinn has so far been 1* 10 hour, 1* 8 hour, 1* 4 hours, 3* 2 hour sessions and still no
ygData.messageBody:
Edd Gross wrote:
>
> > Surely it can't be worse then waiting for the raster ? and then waiting
> > for BrZ and still waiting for BrQ?
>
> I found it much worse... At least in the elder room I could go around a
> kill blue mobs.. In the Gorge EVERYTHING is green. With the help of
> a low level ranger I got bored enough and cleared the zone of all mobs we
> could find on tracking! =)
>
> The other 3 weren't too bad.. The other alchemist in Misty you just camp
> the Motto spawn spot (far left tent). The cube is almost always there,
> and the last one I guess he spawns all the time.

Br Z took me 3* 8 hour session and 3* 2 hours session to find. Br Qwinn
has so far been 1* 10 hour, 1* 8 hour, 1* 4 hours, 3* 2 hour sessions
and still no sign of him. And there is absolutely nothing blue for me to
kill in SKaranas, I sit just south of the entrance to Paw doing nothing,
save the occasion ooc ("anyone seen Br Qwinn?"). Oddly if I get a
response (which is rarely) I get "I haven't seen him since 2 patches
ago" or "I haven't seen him in over a week".

I spent 70 hours trying to get a gnome toy from Nilits Contraption (for
the kerran toy) before giving up, it was slightly better then skaranas
atleast I felt like I was increasing my chances by killing everything
that moved outside the mino caves. The really stupid thing is the guy
you talk to, to get the clue as to what to kill says "Talk not now! My
creation runs wild!" .... hmmm no ... no it certainly is not running
wild.
